    • withWheelBase

      public DrivetrainConfig.DrivetrainConfigBuilder withWheelBase(edu.wpi.first.units.measure.Distance wheelBase)
      Set the wheel base of the drivetrain.

      This value should be set to the distance between the centers of the left and right wheels on the drivetrain in meters. This value is used by the drivetrain to calculate its linear velocity.
